  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a xcb-util-wm</title>

    <para>
      The <application>xcb-util-wm</application> package contains libraries which
provide client and window-manager helpers for EWMH and ICCCM.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

