  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de xcb-util-wm</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>xcb-util-wm</application> executando os seguintes
comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure $XORG_CONFIG &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      <!--To test the results, issue:
      <command>
LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$XORG_PREFIX/lib make check</command>.-->
Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
      
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

